#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_features
msgid "<b>360-degree vision</b>"
msgstr "<b>360-graders udsyn</b>"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_features
msgid "<b>Built in mic</b>"
msgstr "<b>Indbygget mikrofon</b>"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_features
msgid "<b>Stunning visuals</b>"
msgstr "<b>Fantastiske billeder</b>"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_image_text
msgid ""
"<font style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--o-color-1) 0%,"
" var(--o-color-2) 100%);\" class=\"text-gradient\">Enter in a new "
"world</font>"
msgstr ""
"<font style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--o-color-1) 0%, "
"var(--o-color-2) 100%);\" class=\"text-gradient\">Træd ind i en ny verden</"
"font>"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_text_image
msgid ""
"<font style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--o-color-1) 0%,"
" var(--o-color-2) 100%);\" class=\"text-gradient\">Full immersion</font>"
msgstr ""
"<font style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--o-color-1) 0%, "
"var(--o-color-2) 100%);\" class=\"text-gradient\">Fuld fordybelse</font>"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_features
msgid "A small explanation of this great feature, in clear words."
msgstr ""
"En kort beskrivelse af disse fantastiske funktioner, formuleret i klare "
"vendinger."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_media_list
msgid "Comfort &amp; Ease"
msgstr "Komfort og lethed"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_color_blocks_2
msgid ""
"Conquer leaderboards, crush workouts, create with friends and more. Get lost"
" in a growing library of VR classics and all-new experiences."
msgstr ""
"Klatr til tops på ranglisterne, gennemfør træningsprogrammer, skab indhold "
"med venner og meget mere. Dyk ned i et stadigt voksende univers af VR-"
"klassikere og spændende nye oplevelser."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_three_columns
msgid "Design"
msgstr "Design"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_numbers
msgid "Different lenses"
msgstr "Forskellige perspektiver"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_cover
msgid "Discover more"
msgstr "Opdag mere"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_picture
msgid "Experience a new world"
msgstr "Oplev en ny verden"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_media_list
msgid "Fitting design"
msgstr "Passende design"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_color_blocks_2
msgid "Freedom"
msgstr "Frihed"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"From design concept to the showroom, create and manage workflows with better"
" collaboration."
msgstr ""
"Fra designkoncept til udstillingslokale: Opret og administrér arbejdsgange "
"med bedre samarbejde."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"From high-risk safety simulations and maintenance procedures to soft skills "
"like public speaking."
msgstr ""
"Fra risikofyldte sikkerhedssimulationer og vedligeholdelsesprocedurer til "
"bløde kompetencer som retorik."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_three_columns
msgid "Gaming"
msgstr "Gaming"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_color_blocks_2
msgid "Multiplayer"
msgstr "Flerbruger"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_media_list
msgid "Natural control"
msgstr "Naturlig kontrol"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_numbers
msgid "New games every week"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_color_blocks_2
msgid ""
"No matter who you are, with a growing library of games and experiences there"
" is no limit to where you can go and what you can do in virtual reality."
msgstr ""
"Uanset hvem du er, er der med et stadigt voksende udvalg af spil og "
"oplevelser ingen grænser for, hvor du kan tage hen, og hvad du kan lave i "
"den virtuelle virkelighed."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_numbers
msgid "Number of controllers"
msgstr "Antal controllere"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_picture
msgid ""
"Put yourself at the center of an extraordinary gaming universe with "
"exclusive games."
msgstr "Træd ind i hjertet af et enestående spilunivers med eksklusive spil."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_numbers
msgid "Storage capacity (GB)"
msgstr "Lagringskapacitet (GB)"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_features
msgid "Tell what's the value for the customer for this feature."
msgstr "Forklar, hvilken værdi denne funktion har for kunden."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_cover
msgid "The Revolution <br/> in Virtual Reality"
msgstr "Revolutionen <br/> i virtual reality"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kea.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designværktøjer"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_three_columns
msgid "Training"
msgstr "Træning"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_media_list
msgid ""
"Use this snippet to build various types of components that feature a left- "
"or right-aligned image alongside textual content. Duplicate the element to "
"create a list that fits your needs."
msgstr ""
"Brug dette kodestykke til at bygge diverse slags komponenter, der indeholder "
"et venstre- eller højre-orienteret billede sammen med tekst indhold. "
"Dupliker elementet for at oprette en liste der passer til dine behov."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"VR takes immersive gaming to another level. From deep environmental "
"interactions to puzzle solving."
msgstr ""
"VR løfter den immersive spiloplevelse til et helt nyt niveau – fra dyb "
"interaktion med omgivelserne til løsning af gåder."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_picture
msgid ""
"Watch as a living game world comes alive all around you, with a seamless "
"field of view wherever you look."
msgstr ""
"Oplev, hvordan en spilverden vågner til live omkring dig og skaber en "
"sammenhængende oplevelse, uanset hvor du kigger hen."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_media_list
msgid ""
"We only use original parts or parts of equivalent quality. ​We make sure you"
" get the best quality available on the market at the best price. All our "
"interventions are guaranteed for a period of one year."
msgstr ""
"Vi bruger udelukkende originale reservedele eller reservedele af tilsvarende "
"kvalitet og sikrer den bedst mulige kvalitet til markedets bedste pris. Der "
"ydes et års garanti på alle reparationer."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_text_image
msgid ""
"Write one or two paragraphs describing your product or services. To be "
"successful your content needs to be useful to your readers."
msgstr ""
"Skriv et eller to afsnit, der beskriver dit produkt eller dine ydelser. Dit "
"indhold har mest effekt, hvis det er nyttigt for dine læsere."

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_features
msgid "Write what the customer would like to know, not what you want to show."
msgstr "Skriv det, kunden gerne vil vide, ikke det, du gerne vil vise."
